I decided to get curtain bangs!!!

Here’s the video that shows you how worried I was while getting this done! I was prepared to go home crying. 😂

I’ve had long hair since forever and I’m not big on experimenting when it comes to haircuts. I wanted to do this since a while but I was super doubtful about how bangs would look on me. After monthsss of overthinking, I finally got it done yesterday and I LOVE IT SO MUCHHHH 

@shimonabangera Thanks for the moral support, I’ve kept the audio as it is only so you can hear her cheering me up in the background 😂❤️

latestIgtvVideos.caption:

It is enriched with the goodness of six flower oils, which makes it so extraordinary!

This is honestly a wonder product for me. Grab yours now and enjoy an additional 5% off on checkout! 🧡
